      <abstract>
        <t>&lt;p&gt;This document defines requirements for IPv6 nodes. It is expected that IPv6 will be deployed in a wide range of devices and situations. Specifying the requirements for IPv6 nodes allows IPv6 to function well and interoperate in a large number of situations and deployments.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This document obsoletes RFC 6434, and in turn RFC 4294.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
